			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				This is a very UNUSEFULL spell for the clerics. When you are fighting solo, if you need to use that spell is because there are 3 mobs on you. Ok, you are dead because that spell only makes around 45 points of damage. And at lvl 19+ mobs has a lot of hit points.<BR>
<BR>
When you are in a group, your mission is to keep all the party alive, if you cast that spell, you are wasting 85 mana points that you can use to heal a tank in a very close future. Tanks can do a minimum of 50 points per round at lvl 19, better for all the party if they can survive with your heal spell. 2 healing spells are 120 mana cost. If you cast one time and begin to meditate for a few seconds, you can cast another healing spell and make your tanks happyes.<BR>
<BR>
<BR>
<BR>
Keep your tanks alive! :)<BR>
Pathito<BR>
19th cleric<BR>
Solusek Ro
				</font>
